SELECT     l_returnflag,     SUM(l_extendedprice * l_discount) AS total_discounted_price FROM     tpch1g.lineitem GROUP BY     l_returnflag;

SELECT   l_returnflag,   l_linestatus,   SUM(l_quantity) AS total_quantity,   SUM(l_extendedprice) AS total_extended_price,   SUM(l_discount) AS total_discount FROM   tpch1g.lineitem GROUP BY   l_returnflag,   l_linestatus;

SELECT   l_returnflag,   l_linestatus,   SUM(l_quantity) AS total_quantity,   SUM(l_extendedprice) AS total_extended_price,   SUM(l_discount) AS total_discount,   SUM(l_tax) AS total_tax,   COUNT(*) AS order_count FROM   tpch1g.lineitem GROUP BY   l_returnflag,   l_linestatus;

SELECT   l_returnflag,   l_linestatus,   SUM(l_quantity) AS total_quantity,   SUM(l_extendedprice) AS total_extended_price,   SUM(l_discount) AS total_discount,   SUM(l_tax) AS total_tax,   SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS total_disc_price,   SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) * (1 + l_tax)) AS total_charge,   COUNT(*) AS order_count FROM   tpch1g.lineitem GROUP BY   l_returnflag,   l_linestatus;

SELECT l.l_orderkey, l.l_partkey, l.l_suppkey, l.l_linenumber, l.l_quantity, l.l_extendedprice, l.l_discount, l.l_tax, l.l_returnflag, l.l_linestatus, l.l_shipdate, l.l_commitdate, l.l_receiptdate, l.l_shipinstruct, l.l_shipmode, o.o_orderdate, o.o_orderpriority, o.o_clerk, o.o_shippriority, c.c_name, c.c_address, c.c_phone, c.c_acctbal, p.p_name, p.p_mfgr, p.p_brand, p.p_type, p.p_size, p.p_container, s.s_name, s.s_address, s.s_phone, s.s_acctbal, n.n_name, r.r_name FROM lineitem l JOIN orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey JOIN customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey JOIN part p ON l.l_partkey = p.p_partkey JOIN supplier s ON l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey JOIN nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey JOIN region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey;

SELECT l.l_orderkey, l.l_partkey, l.l_suppkey, l.l_quantity, l.l_extendedprice, l.l_discount, o.o_orderdate, c.c_name, p.p_name, s.s_name FROM lineitem l JOIN orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey JOIN customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey JOIN part p ON l.l_partkey = p.p_partkey JOIN supplier s ON l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey;

SELECT l.l_orderkey, l.l_partkey, l.l_suppkey, l.l_quantity, l.l_extendedprice, l.l_discount, o.o_orderdate, c.c_name, p.p_name, s.s_name, n.n_name FROM lineitem l JOIN orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey JOIN customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey JOIN part p ON l.l_partkey = p.p_partkey JOIN supplier s ON l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey JOIN nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey;
